snippet.title: Zoo Tycoon (2001) (Microsoft) Commercial
snippet.description: here is a commercial that I remember seeing back as a child, this is the Zoo Tycoon computer game from 2001 which features a family having a lot of zoo animals living in there house. also I use to have this game but not anymore since I donated to a thrift store like goodwill or something but i'm okay with that!
